|Inferences={{Inference
|Inference.Description=The ability of the machine to function (operating_x-schema execution) depends on the state of its physical structure (functional_status).  If a machine is broken, it will not function.  If it is 'well-oiled' it will perform more efficiently than if it is 'rusty'.
